      "cooked": "<p>Revista angleze dyshon se rusët po përzihen në punët e brendshme të Serbisë e Malit të Zi. Atentat i mundshëm ndaj kryeministrit serb dhe puç gjatë zgjedhjeve</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.economist.com/europe/2016/11/04/russia-appears-to-cause-trouble-in-the-balkans?fsrc=scn%2Ftw_ec%2Frussia_appears_to_cause_trouble_in_the_balkans\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/1/7/17019984dfbba07de5ee5ef51f02e44ab752d031.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.economist.com/europe/2016/11/04/russia-appears-to-cause-trouble-in-the-balkans?fsrc=scn%2Ftw_ec%2Frussia_appears_to_cause_trouble_in_the_balkans\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Economist</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:595/335;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/8/f/8f7e97e79779ab539a4720e287220bbf9a33f9a7.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"595\" height=\"335\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.economist.com/europe/2016/11/04/russia-appears-to-cause-trouble-in-the-balkans?fsrc=scn%2Ftw_ec%2Frussia_appears_to_cause_trouble_in_the_balkans\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Russia appears to cause trouble in the Balkans</a></h3>\n\n  <p>But with few independent media outlets, the truth can prove elusive</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Konkluzioni më interesant i artikullit: shumica e artikujve në mediat popullore serbe e malazeze janë të pavërteta.</p>",
